OL,3,CGuernsey financial adviser helped hide
OL,4,Cmillions for 'Butcher of Hama'
OL,6,FThe uncle of Syria's former president
OL,7,F- known as the "butcher of Hama" -
OL,8,Fused a Guernsey adviser to secretly
OL,9,Fmanage his wealth, a joint
OL,10,Finvestigation has revealed.
OL,12,FRifaat al-Assad, the uncle of Bashar
OL,13,Fal-Assad, collaborated with Guernsey
OL,14,Ffinancial consultant Ginette Louise
OL,15,FBlondel to manage millions of his
OL,16,Ffunds.
