OL,6,FThe joint investigation from The
OL,7,FGuardian and The Bureau of
OL,8,FInvestigative Journalism reported
OL,9,FRifaat's wealth included "a large
OL,10,FEuropean property empire worth
OL,11,Fhundreds of millions of euros that
OL,12,Fprosecutors claim was acquired with
OL,13,Ffunds looted from the wartorn state."
OL,15,FIt comes as Guernsey waits for the
OL,16,Fresults of an assessment conducted by
OL,17,Fanti-money laundering body, Moneyval.
