OL,6,FRifaat al-Assad is the uncle of former
OL,7,FSyrian leader, Bashar al-Assad, who
OL,8,Fwas overthrown by the rebel offensive,
OL,9,Fending the Assad family's 50-year iron
OL,10,Frule on Sunday 8 December.
OL,12,FRifaat has been dubbed the "butcher of
OL,13,FHama" for what the report describes as
OL,14,F"his alleged role overseeing the
OL,15,Funlawful imprisonment, torture and
OL,16,Fexecution of between 10,000 and 40,000
OL,17,Fpeople in 1982".
