OL,3,CGuernsey financial adviser helped hide
OL,4,Cmillions for 'Butcher of Hama'
OL,6,FIn March 2024, Ginette Blondel was
OL,7,Ffined #210,000 and banned from the
OL,8,Findustry for nine years after she
OL,9,Fknowingly worked for an "alleged war
OL,10,Fcriminal" - however it was not clear
OL,11,Fwho this was.
OL,13,FThe unnamed man - named Client 1 - was
OL,14,Fdescribed as "high-risk" and "an
OL,15,Falleged war criminal".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/10
