OL,3,CGuernsey financial adviser helped hide
OL,4,Cmillions for 'Butcher of Hama'
OL,6,FIt followed a two-and-a-half-year
OL,7,Finvestigation by Guernsey's Financial
OL,8,FServices Commission (FSC) which ruled
OL,9,Fthat Ms Blondel "consistently failed
OL,10,Fto understand the gravity and
OL,11,Fconsequences of her actions" and
OL,12,F"caused reputational damage to the
OL,13,FBailiwick as an international finance
OL,14,Fcentre".
OL,16,FOn one occasion, the investigation
OL,17,Funcovered that Ms Blondel received E1
OL,18,Fmillion into her personal bank account
OL,19,Ffrom a company owned by Client 1 to
OL,20,Fset up a proposed Guernsey trust
OL,21,Fcompany.
OL,26,@yD@dOk
