OL,6,FThis did not go ahead and Ms Blondel
OL,7,Finstead used the money to make more
OL,8,Fthan 150 payments to multiple third
OL,9,Fparties on behalf of her client.
OL,11,FThe FSC believes this "led to a very
OL,12,Freal risk that Ms Blondel may have
OL,13,Fbeen used to launder the proceeds of
OL,14,Fcrime, a risk which Ms Blondel has
OL,15,Fconsistently failed to recognise".
