OL,4,Cmillions for 'Butcher of Hama'
OL,6,FA statement from the States of
OL,7,FGuernsey - the island's government -
OL,8,Freads: "As a jurisdiction, Guernsey
OL,9,Ftakes money laundering, proliferation
OL,10,Ffinancing and any other unlawful
OL,11,Fconduct in the financial sphere
OL,12,Fextremely seriously. The systems we
OL,13,Fhave in place for regulation and law
OL,14,Fenforcement reflect this stance.
OL,16,F"In this specific case, the Guernsey
OL,17,FFinancial Services Commission ` the
OL,18,Flocal regulator - took serious action
OL,19,Fagainst this individual, handing down
OL,20,Fa very large fine and a ban from
OL,21,Fworking in the industry.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/10
