PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F388A1734501718
OL,3,CGuernsey financial adviser helped hide
OL,4,Cmillions for 'Butcher of Hama'
OL,6,F"However, as people working in the law
OL,7,Fenforcement sector are well aware, the
OL,8,Fevidential threshold for a criminal
OL,9,Fprosecution and the threshold for a
OL,10,Fregulator to take action are very
OL,11,Fdifferent.
OL,13,F"Guernsey's Economic & Financial Crime
OL,14,FBureau (EFCB) does not comment on
OL,15,Finvestigations relating to a named
OL,16,Findividual. However, as a general
OL,17,Fcomment, the EFCB investigates all
OL,18,Fmatters diligently and in accordance
OL,19,Fwith the law where there is any
OL,20,Fsuspicion of criminal activity.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/10
