OL,6,F"As part of the Bailiwick of
OL,7,FGuernsey's long-term commitment to
OL,8,Fthis area, we have a National Strategy
OL,9,Ffor combatting financial crime. This
OL,10,Fis a published document, despite there
OL,11,Fbeing no requirement within the FATF
OL,12,Fstandards to publish a national
OL,13,Fstrategy, as we consider it important
OL,14,Fto articulate our position for the
OL,15,Fbenefit of domestic and international
OL,16,Fstakeholders.
