OL,6,F"This strategy and the joint efforts
OL,7,Fof our regulator and law enforcement
OL,8,Fagencies ensure we are a modern and
OL,9,Fwell-regulated finance jurisdiction.
OL,10,FThis case is evidence of our
OL,11,Fstrategy's effectiveness, with
OL,12,Fregulatory and law enforcement
OL,13,Fauthorities working together and
OL,14,Fensuring action is taken where it is
OL,15,Fpossible to do so."
OL,17,FITV News has reached out to Ms Blondel
OL,18,Ffor comment.
